# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok russian parliament 's upper chamber announced wednesday it has overridden a presidential veto and passed into law a bill claiming art seized in germany at the end of world war ii as russia 's property .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Upper"
                  :op2 "Chamber")
            :part-of (g2 / government-organization
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Parliament")
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Russia"))))
      :ARG1 (a2 / and
            :op1 (o / override-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (v / veto-01
                        :ARG0 (p / president)))
            :op2 (p2 / pass-01
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (b / bill
                        :ARG0-of (c2 / claim-02
                              :ARG1 (p3 / property
                                    :poss c
                                    :domain (a3 / art
                                          :ARG1-of (s / seize-01
                                                :location (c3 / country
                                                      :name (n4 / name
                                                            :op1 "Germany"))
                                                :time (e / end-01
                                                      :ARG1 (w / war
                                                            :name (n5 / name
                                                                  :op1 "World"
                                                                  :op2 "War"
                                                                  :op3 "II"))))))))
                  :prep-into (l / law)))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the international cricket council postponed the champions trophy tournament in pakistan on sunday after teams expressed security concerns and threatened to pull out if the eight-nation competition went ahead .
# ::alignments
(p / postpone-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "International"
                  :op2 "Cricket"
                  :op3 "Council"))
      :ARG1 (t / tournament
            :mod (t2 / trophy
                  :poss (c / champion))
            :location (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Pakistan")))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s / sunday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (e / express-01
                        :ARG0 (t3 / team)
                        :ARG1 (c3 / concern-01
                              :ARG0 (s2 / security)
                              :ARG1 t3))
                  :op2 (t4 / threaten-01
                        :ARG0 t3
                        :ARG1 (p2 / pull-out-02
                              :ARG1 t3
                              :condition (g / go-06
                                    :ARG0 (c4 / compete-01
                                          :ARG0 (n3 / nation
                                                :quant 8))
                                    :ARG2 (a3 / ahead)))))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (m / ministry
            :topic (ii / interior))
      :ARG1 (b / behead-01
            :ARG0 (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Saudi"
                        :op2 "Arabia"))
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "India")))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Iraq")))
                  :op3 (p3 / person
                        :mod (c4 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Pakistan"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (m2 / monday))
            :time (a2 / after
                  :op1 (c5 / convict-01
                        :ARG1 a
                        :ARG2 (s2 / smuggle-01
                              :ARG0 a
                              :ARG1 (d2 / drug))))))

                              :name (n3 / name

                                    :quant 3

                  :ARG1 (f / film
                        :name (n / name

                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 " atom"
                                    :op2 " egoyan"))
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)))
            :ARG2 (l / live-01
                  :manner (t / through
                        :op1 (e / event
                              :mod (t2 / turbulent)
                              :ARG1-of (d / depict-01
                                    :ARG0 f))))
            :degree (r2 / rather)))

(c / close-01
      :ARG1 (ii / index
            :mod (c2 / composite)
            :poss (c3 / company
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "China"))
            :location (e / exchange-01
                  :ARG1 (s / stock)
                  :location (c4 / city
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Shanghai")))
            :mod (b / benchmark))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :ARG1-of (u / up-02
            :ARG3 (o / or
                  :op1 (p / point)
                  :op2 (p2 / percentage-entity
                        :value ".##"))
            :ARG4 (c5 / close-01
                  :time (p3 / previous))))
